\id 2TH Tagin: Bible Translation 1st Edition
\h 2 Tesalonian
\toc1 TESALONIAN vdwa Paul gv Siti Lvnyinvbv jinam
\toc2 2 Tesalonian
\toc3 2Tes
\mt1 TESALONIAN
\mt2 vdwa Paul gv Siti Lvnyinvbv Jinam
\imt1 Mintamchonam
\ip Tesalonika gvrja lo mvngjwngnv vdwv Kristo gv aakur kunam ha dvmin lakula kaayala doonam lvkwng ngv mingominpenla minyakunam mv adwkakubv ribwng toku. \bk Paul gv Tesalonian vdwa siti jidvnam\bk* si Ahtu gv aadw alu hv aaro pvku vla minam go. Paul um sibv minbwk jitoku, Kristo gv aatv madvbv alvmanv okv achialvbv alvmabv rigvnv “Alvmaya choknv” vla minam gvlokv, hv Kristonyi rinyingriru riku.
\ip Apostol Paul so puririnv vdwa dinchinv gaam vkv minpa jidu, adwkaku okv hirukaya nga mvngnga gvrila mvngjwng yanga haatin yala Paul la okv ninyigv lvkobv kudungkua ribam vdwgv rinam apiabv turnam lvgabv kudungkua rila doolakv vtoku.
\iot Arwng lokv darlinnam
\io1 Mimtamchonam \ior (1:1-2) \ior*
\io1 Hartv okv ayumnam gaam \ior (1:3-12)\ior*
\io1 Kristo gv aakur kuse gv lvkwng nga minam \ior (2:1-17) \ior*
\io1 Kristan ridungsvngdung nga tamsarnam \ior (3:1-15) \ior*
\io1 Minyakunam \ior (3:16-18) \ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Nyim 17:1\x* Paul, Sailas okv Timoti gvlokv—Tesalonika gv gvrja gv nyi yvvbunudw Abu Pwknvyarnv okv Ahtu Jisu Kristo gvbvrinv vdwa jidunv:
\p 
\v 2 Pwknvyarnv Abu okv Ahtu Jisu Kristo nonua aya okv sarsopoyo nga jigv nyika.
\s1 Kristo gv aarilo jwngkadakanam
\p 
\v 3 Ngonugv ajin vdwa, ngonu nonugv lvgabv Pwknvyarnvnyi dw mvnwnglo umbonyikv vdubv rirung dunv. So si ngonugv vbvridubv alvnv dw vku, ogulvgavbolo nonunogv mvngjwng ngv achialvbv kaiyaya duku okv nonuno akin-akinhv kvvbi am paknam rinam gvnam hvka kaiyaya duku.
\v 4 Vkvlvgabv ngonu atubongv Pwknvyarnv gv gvrja vdwlo ngonu goosu dunv. Ngonu nonunogv mvritmvka okv hirukaya mvnwngnga saktv sula okv mvngjwng bvngla rikunama ngonu goosu dunv.
\v 5 Svbvrinam mvnwng sokv gaklin duku Pwknvyarnv gv jwngkadaka ngv jvjv duku, vbvrinam lokv kaapa duku nonugv hirukaya hinla rinam hv nonu Pwknvyarnv gv Karv lo aala dukubv riduku.
\v 6 Jvjv ngv ogu vdw um Pwknvyarnv rire: nonua hirukaya monv nga hv bunua hirukaya naalwk jire.
\v 7 Okv hv nonu ngonua hirukaya kunvnga saknu nama jireku, vdwlo Jisu nwgv kairungnv nyidogindung nga lvkobv nyidomooku tolo daklin rikudw hv so vdw sum rireku,
\v 8 okv hv vmv nga gudor dukubv bvngla ikula Pwknvyarnvnyi toa kunv vdwa okv Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv lvkwngbv Alvnv Yunying nga tvvmanv vdwa mvrit dukubv rireku.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Aij 2:10\x* Bunua hirukaya himbwng jikulo mvrit riku, okv Ahtu gv nvchi okv kairungnv gwlwk lokv adu moreku,
\v 10 Vdwlo nwgv nyi vdwa naarwk tvbv ho Alu lo aarikudw ninyi mvngjwngnv nyi mvnwng lokv hartvnama okv mvngdv nama paareku. Ho nonuka reming gvvre, ogulvgavbolo nonu ngonugv minji kunam doin am jvjv ngv vla mvngjwng toku.
\v 11 Vkvlvgabv ngonu lokia nonugv lvgabv kumdunv. Ngonugv Pwknvyarnv gv nonua singlakv vla goknam lo singla dubv rimutvka vla ngonu ninyia koodunv. Nonugv alvnam gv lvgabv mvngnam ha hv richi molaka okv nonugv mvngjwngla kudungkua rinam ha rinya molaka.
\v 12 Vbvrila Ahtu Jisu gv\f + \fr 1:12 \fqa ngonugv Pwnvyarnv okv Ahtu gv; \ft Vmalo\fqa ngonugv Pwnvyarnv okv Ahtu\f* aminv nonu gvlo hartvnama paadubv okv nonu ninyi gvlokv paadubv, ngonugv Pwknvyarnv gvla okv Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv aya lokv.
\c 2
\s1 Alvmanv Angv
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1Tes 4:15-17\x*Ngonugv Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv aakur kuse gv lvkwng nga okv ngonugv ninyia lvkobv doopam pamse nga minrinyi: ngoogv ajin vdwa ngo nonua koodwkrwkla mindunv,
\v 2 nonugv mvngnamlo mvngpumvngpa bv mvngbwkgolo manv gubv riyoka vmalo Ahtu gv Alu hv looro pvku vla mvngru mabvka. So si mvngka kunamv vbvka ripvnvpv nyikrw kaarilo vmalo japkar rilo minpvnvpv vmalo ngonu siti loka lvkpvnv vla kvvbi gunv minpvnvpv.
\v 3 Nonuno yvvnyika kupku yoka. Vdwlo ataranyabv Nyiru rumisinamv rilin maredw okv Alvmanv Angv uyumooku bolo dooji kunv angv daklwk maredw ho Alu hv loomare.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Dan 11:36; Eje 28:2\x*Hv pwknvyarnv gubv rinv mvnwngnga vmalo kumnamjonam dvdv nga rikin reku okv atu hv ho mvnwngnga kaiyanv gubv minsureku. Hv Pwknvyarnv gv Pwknvyarnvnaam lo vnglwkla okv doolwkdula okv Pwknvyarnv gubv minsure.
\p 
\v 5 Nonuno mvngpa malare? Ngo nonua lvkobv doorilo so mvnwng sum nonua minpa jipv kunv.
\v 6 Rigvrila vjak sum rilin moma dubv rinv vkv doodu, okv si ogu vdw um nonuno chindu. Vbvrikunamv ridw lo Alvmanv Angv daklwk reku.
\v 7 Chinyumanam Alvmanv gv jwkrw hv kudungkua nga rirapla ridungduku. Vbvritola ogugo ritv dukudw hv rikumare, okv um lamtv loka naalinla naa ma dvdvlobv.
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Aij 11:4\x*Vbvrikunamv Alvmanv Angv daklwk reku, vbvritola vdwlo Ahtu Jisu aari kudw ninyigv gaam gv saknam lokv ninyia sakki reku okv ninyigv loung unglit lokv ninyia ungyak reku.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Mt 24:24\x*Alvmanv Angv Uyu gv jwkrw nga lvkobv aagvlai kula mvvnamrunam bv nvgwngnv lamrwpanam okv kaasartabobv rila kaatam reku,
\v 10 okv ngeji kunv nyi vdwa nvgwngnv kupnv nvnv rinvla kupre. Bunu nyereku ogulvgavbolo bunu Ringjikunv jvjv nga alvbv torwk sima.
\v 11 Vkvlvgabv Pwknvyarnv bunu gvlo mvvnam gv jwkrw nga jilula bunua mvvnam ha mvngjwng motoku.
\v 12 Vbvrinam gv anyung ngv mvnwngngv yvvbunudw jvjv nga mvngjwng manv, vbvritola rimurlo himpu pumin karnv vdwa ngoomu dukubv ritoku.
\p 
\v 13 Ahtu gv paknam ajin vdwa, ngonu nonugv lvgabv Pwknvyarnvnyi alu gv dwkia umbonyikv vrung sego ogulvgavbolo nonugv jvjv nga mvngjwng lokv Pwknvyarnv nonua Dow gv jwkrw lokv ninyigv darwknv nyi bv mvnam lvgabv ringlin kunamlo nonua \f + \fr 2:13 \fqa atukchongv aingbv; \ft Megonv kitaplo doodu \fqa atuake gv lokv\f*darcho linpv kunv.
\v 14 Ngonugv nonua Alvnv Yunying japji kolokv Pwknvyarnv nonua gokpv kunv; Pwknvyarnv nonua goknam mv Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv yunglinamlo nonugv baag ka paamu dubv vla goktoku.
\v 15 Vkvlvgabv ngonugv ajin vdwa nonuno ngonugv japjila okv siti bv lvkla rinam ho gv jvjv lo bikubiv mabv gakbwngla doonya laka.
\p 
\v 16 Ngonugv Ahtu Jisu Kristo atubongv okv ngonugv Pwknvyarnv Abu, ngonua paknv okv ninyigv ayalo ngonua mvngrw ha jibwngnv okv biv manv mvngtin ha jinv,
\v 17 nonua mintvmirula alu gv dwkia alvnv ogu vdw um mindu ridubv gwlwk a jilaka.
\c 3
\s1 Ngonugv lvgabv Kumlaka
\p 
\v 1 Ataranyabv, ngonugv ajin vdwa, ngonugv lvgabv kumlaka, Ahtu gv doinv nonugv hoka rinam apiabv baapubv dusik kardubv okv nyi vdwv doin ha mvngdvla naarwksinam lvgabv.
\v 2 Okv ngonua Pwknvyarnv alvmanv nyi loka ringya dubv kumji talaka; ogulvgavbolo doin ha tvvnv nyi dvdv ngv mvngjwng dunv vnam kaama.
\p 
\v 3 Vbvritola Ahtu mvngtin dubv rinv ngv, okv nw nonua Alvmanv Angv loka ringyare okv mvngrw dubv mvre.
\v 4 Okv Ahtu ngonua jidu nonua mvngtin dubv, okv ngonu nonua ogugo mindudw um nonu ridungdo okv ribwngre vla ngonu nonua mvngtin dunv.
\p 
\v 5 Ahtu nonua rigvdakgvla Pwknvyarnv gv paknam ha okv Kristo gv saktv jinam ha kaiyayabv chindubv jigv nyika.
\s1 Kudungkua Rirung svngv
\p 
\v 6 Ngonugv ajin vdwa, ngonu nonua Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv amin lokv mindunv nonuno vkvnv ajin vdwa adu silaka yvvbunudw sepelakrela okv ngonugv minam ha tvvla rimanv vdwa.
\v 7 Nonuno atubongv alvbv chinsudo ngonu ogugo ripvdw um nonu riming gvvrung svngv. Ngonu nonua lvkobv rirelo ngonu sepelakre matoku.
\v 8 Ngonu arv jimabv yvv gvka ridur ha anyubv naarwk simato. Vmabvya ngonu atubongv raaibv kudungkua nga gvlwkbv rise nga risuto; ogulvgavbolo ngonu nonua yvvnyika ngonugv lvgabv dormu nwngma mvngla kudungkua nga aluayu bv risuto.
\v 9 Ngonugv vbvrinamv ngonu nonua ridur go koonyu rinyu manamgo doola ripvnv vnam kaama; ngonugv vbvrinamv nonua kaagvla riming gvmu dubv vla ripvnv.
\v 10 Ngonugv nonua lvkobv doorilo, ngonu nonua vbv minkito, “Yvvdw kudungkua riji makv vdunv um dvnam dvmu yoka.”
\p 
\v 11 Ngonu vbv minto ogulvgavbolo nonugv ara lo nyi mego sepelakrela oguguka rimabv dominla kvvbinyi vdwgv korvpachu riku lo mingominpin riala ridu vla ngonu tvvpado.
\v 12 Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv amin lokv ngonu so nyi vdwa dinda bv singla atubogv singdung lvgabv pwla paala relaka vla mindunv.
\p 
\v 13 Vbvritola ajin vdwa nonuno alvnv kudungkua rikulo agarapi rungyoka.
\v 14 Ngonugv nonua siti jinam so gv doin a akonv tvvmabv rinv ngv doi nvpv. Vbvrinv go dobolo, ninyia oguguka ribamdakbam yoka kaagapla kaapv laka, vkvlvgavbolo ninyia hinying modubv.
\v 15 Vbvritola ninyia nyirunv aingbv riyo miyoka; vmabvya ajinamin bv gamrw yalaka.
\s1 Minyabv minam gamchar vdwv
\p 
\v 16 Ahtu atubongv, ngonugv sarsopoyo gv lvtwngbv rinv, dw mvnwnglo okv lamtv mvnwnglo nonua sarsopoyo nga jigv nyika. Ahtu nonu mvnwngnga lvkobv dooming gvlaka.
\p 
\v 17 Ngo atubogv laak lo sum lvkdunv: Paul lokv kumrwknama jidunv, svbv ngo lvknam ha ngo svbv dvdvbv lvkdunv.
\p 
\v 18 Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv aya ngv nonu mvnwnglo dooming gvlaka.
